frs.broker

Interface ClientProxy


  • public interface ClientProxy
    The ClientProxy role in the Broker pattern. This is just a marker interface as the set of methods is defined by which ever interface the proxy implements.

    Responsibility: To translate any method calls into RequestObjects that are forwarded to a Requestor instance.
